skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: namaskar yoga
des:
Welcome to Sadhguru's Namaskar Yoga. This skill allows you to play a 3 minute video of Sadhguru's yoga for all. You can control this skill by using Play and stop.

It features prominent faces around the globe doing Namaskar, which is the simplest of form yoga. By putting your hands together, you can bring harmony within yourself and with the world around you.

If you love this skill, please let us know by giving us a 5-star rating!
